Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:15.84,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:20.38,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:24.92,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:38.00,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:46.41,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:53.75,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:58.55,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:05.56,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:15.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:23.05,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:27.78,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:34.72,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. It's too girlish for a yacht.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm... Not good enough, just too ordinary...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this? You'll be a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it too childish?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... You're right. It looks like {\i1}Shichi-go-san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a bit more serious, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous! A party aboard a yacht!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then dinner at a restaurant overlooking the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That yacht is Miya-sama's family boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hieeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hieeee" is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mid-terms are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With lightened hearts, we went shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko was helping me find a dress for the Sorority party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end of mid-term break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow the results get posted on the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...listing everyone from the first in the class,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...all the way down to number two-hundred-something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aiming for a little above the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Not to stand out, nor be looked down upon", is my motto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not the same for you, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to rank in the top 50 to stay a Sorority member, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But thank God! I'm so grateful now that I wasn't "Sorority Quality".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, you'll be okay! I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smart! You'll be 43rd, no... 38th...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My predictions are pretty good! You could call me "the Psychic Girl".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, my Dear Brother... mid-terms are over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The glare of the sun grows stronger each day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I sense that the season is about to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,15. Fukiko; The Sea Rumbles
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it! You easily made the top 50!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Shinobu-san, you made it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Junko, it's okay... considering the circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to her? She's been at the top since Junior High...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... she's the one who had a high fever on the first day of mid-terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and was hardly even able to write her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then she did pretty well... placing in the top 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Top 70? That's still better than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:12.29,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,We had been digging in silence perhaps an hour and a half,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.02,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...when the dog began to bark loudly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else will happen now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mid-terms are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, 3 months after entering Seiran,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...I must admit that I'm getting more used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else will happen now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...or at least, I won't let anything overwhelm me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finally feeling more confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The matter of Saint-Juste-sama and Miya-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Kaoru-no-Kimi's health...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...even though I may not fully understand these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...I think perhaps I am finally becoming more fond, bit by bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...of Seiran's solemn buildings and foreboding trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, something happened that afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the Sorority House, something I couldn't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now commence this emergency session of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The agenda concerns our Sorority's standings in the mid-term exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The chairperson will be Ichinomiya Fukiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, it was as if a verdict were being delivered at a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as pitiless as the sentencing of a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior member Nakaya Junko-san of section C...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is regrettable we had to convene this emergency session,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...just so we could deal with your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am very truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,First foreign language placed 56th; second foreign language 48th;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Literature 77; politics and economy 63;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mathematics 82; sociology 85;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Statistical analysis 38. The total result 73rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct, Nakaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All our members placed in the top 50 of their class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Except you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the Sorority rules, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate you couldn't meet our standards even for one term.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However, since it would be heartless to expel you so abruptly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...you have one week to resign voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The next scheduled meeting is in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama! Miya-sama, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise that I'll do really well on the finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait until then! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The resignation may be mailed... addressed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiryu-san, Hayashida-san, please vouch for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her I had a high fever during the mid-terms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! It's true, Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san was really, really sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you reconsider her case?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's not fair to pass judgment based on only a single test period.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, really! It's... it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very high-minded of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sorority members are responsible for their health as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no excuse for these shameful results.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This touches upon the pride of the Sorority. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, I wonder if you realize who arranged for your admission!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I keep telling you, you mustn't oppose the will of Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, I wonder if you realize who arranged for your admission!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize what a mistake it would be to make Miya-sama angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen... why not take her some of her favorite red roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you should apologize to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't I admitted on my own merit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you realize who arranged for your admission!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who?" Who was it? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand why, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even attend the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have been chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't permit such an injustice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Injustice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no injustice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If not by an injustice, how could it have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There were fifteen candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of dirty tricks did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even attend the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't agree with this! It isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do for this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed! It's at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have sensitive skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The skin's worst enemy is actually salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mona-Lisa-sama, Vampanera-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nakaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bad girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Freshmen shouldn't come to a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I came all this way to speak to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...and... both of you have been so kind to me... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you... could you ask Miya-sama to reconsider? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but doing such a thing would reflect badly on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me treat you to some tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama! Miya-sama! Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Red roses... Please, Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, my father has a yacht, too! Not quite as big though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'll ask him to take all of us out, Tomoko and you and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you, Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she on her way out, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've really been looking forward to today's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mid-terms are over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san was too, I would imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better worry about yourself instead of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you apologize to Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring red roses to Miya-sama as I suggested?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san was expelled solely on Miya-sama's authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case... could it have been on her authority...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I was selected for the Sorority?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now... I'd thought I was elected fairly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...by open voting, though there might have been a little something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Still that was what I tried to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was beginning to feel some confidence, here at Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'm going to open the champagne! Let's toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the people whose birthdays are this month...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiryu-san, Suzuka-san, and Ukawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you been worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,about what I said the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your selection as a Sorority member was done fairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I regret what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I got upset when you talked back, and I acted meanly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that your recommendation came from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you were chosen by all the sophomore's votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was rather cruel of me to say such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...knowing that you'd been hurt by rumors already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Asking me to forgive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair is so soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Her snow-white, almost translucent skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cool, faraway gaze that is sometimes in her eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks somewhat like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...Saint Juste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they are indeed sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama and Saint-Juste-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,These many dimensions of Miya-sama I saw tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...are even more complex and mysterious
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...than those of Saint-Juste-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...darker than midnight, yet even sorrowful, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I doubt that you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...might you happen to have a boyfriend you are seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I have a pen-pal... I asked him to be like my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You do? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cease at once. It's too early for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All I said was "yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not right, even from Miya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Deciding to whom I will write is something only I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...as well as deciding who shall be my pen-pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll still write you... of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is to not tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...and there's no way she can find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why would she make such a demand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, had enough? You "Yacht-Girl"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo! I just got back and finished changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a report! What's new?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything happen? Any gossip?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... there was something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, yes and no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was sort of so-so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... so-so. The ocean breeze was tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry! I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn interruptions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, where are you going? It's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To see a friend! Up around the corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to call you so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I really needed to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to leave the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I sent my resignation to Miya-sama by express mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've looked longingly at the Sorority for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...since I was in Junior High... and even before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Such beautiful Sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And such chosen, fortunate people... so splendid and magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, I thought, their character had a goodness to match their beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't explain how it changed, but now it seems more like a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been only three months since I joined the Sorority,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but was there anything good that happened to me, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I've resented you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Miya-sama seemed to favor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is a flower that will never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. For speaking up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful. I won't ever forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the Sorority that much, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.95,0:23:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This season, a season of fairy tales, has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.56,0:24:14.76,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:20.23,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.70,0:24:25.84,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:31.31,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.05,0:24:37.59,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.59,0:24:43.06,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:45.79,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.79,0:24:48.60,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:51.00,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.00,0:24:56.27,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.90,0:25:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day of the basketball game,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.84,0:25:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi suffers a bloody foul and must leave the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.89,0:25:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko then panics and follows Kaoru-no-Kimi to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.68,0:25:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There, Kaoru-no-Kimi's words bring tears to Mariko's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.74,0:25:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Comeback
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.15,0:25:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
